Subject: [PATCH] dts: gs201: gpu: Set system-coherency to ACE_LITE

Allow the GPU to be configured for IO Coherency.

Note: This was initially added in If2e3a7e2 and reverted in Ifbd1dcbb1.
Test: 10000 hours SST (b/271438225#comment17)
Bug: 200555454
Change-Id: I5901de8209f26e7860060d8e3f5068fb237708e7
Signed-off-by: Varad Gautam <varadgautam@google.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/google/gs201-gpu.dtsi | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/google/gs201-gpu.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/google/gs201-gpu.dtsi
index b2f98d42e13f..9589f175e8f5 100644
